(OOC: Earth2025 Pantron was nearly destroyed, putting his spark back in him 
will not magically heal him, it was taken out in order to save him, because 
he was dying, remember he was shot at least twice in the head at point blank 
range.)

::Primal Prime::

    "Is anyone here?" He called out to the Ark. He hoped someone would 
answer. He stood in the forest hoping to get the attention of someone. (Just 
so you guys know he's not bigger than a normal sized Transformer, he's like 
first season Primal big.) He transformed into Ground assault mode and went 
around to see where the doors are, soon he found them. He Transformed back to 
Robot mode and walked up to the doors.
    The doors scanned him and then they opened as if they recognized him! He 
couldn't understand this at all, he had never been here before why would they 
recognize him. Now thinking this was some form of trap he backed away, very 
slowly. 
    He pressed a button on his arm. "Umm...If any Maximals pick this up 
please come and find me, my name is..." What is my name? He couldn't 
remember, the only thing he could think of was Prim-He couldn't remember the 
rest, but looking at this place and how primal it is he decided to be Primal 
for the time being.
    "My name is Primal," He said into the comm. Now he waited for a Maximal 
to pick it up and come and find him.
